<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>New Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Added Time of Day Hue Intensity and Weather Hue Override sliders so dawn, dusk, night, and weather tints can
        be tuned past the default subtle blend</li>
      <li>Added an FXMaster particle speed multiplier so weather effects can be sped up or slowed down across all
        Calendaria presets, with active scenes resyncing on change</li>
      <li>Added new module-developer hooks and API methods for theme and ambience integration</li>
      <li>Secondary calendar headers, cross-calendar subheaders, day-cell tooltips, and note-sheet equivalent dates now
        show the live current time and refresh as time advances</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Bulk calendar imports no longer open a note sheet for each imported note, preventing UI freezes on large
        imports</li>
      <li>Calendar exports now include user-created festivals, so they survive a round trip through export and import
      </li>
      <li>Moons with odd cycle lengths now show all phases correctly instead of one phase swallowing the whole cycle,
        and moon anchors with Reset Cycle disabled are honored as soft calibration</li>
      <li>Player HUD now hides or shows immediately when switching to a scene with a different player-visibility flag,
        instead of requiring a reload</li>
      <li>Player-triggered weather randomization now produces varied results instead of always returning the same preset
      </li>
    </ul>

  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
